plyTime":"2018-08-10T03:27:10.000Z","msg":"一個屋企五六個人睇到都燥"},{"pid":"2e5b8ad45fe3a5078e67a82288181302ea06268b","tid":773774,"uid":121610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T03:32:57.000Z","msg":"幾有planning 係樓個yield太低<br />\n應該搵間高yield d 舊樓/other fixed income products"},{"pid":"59974fca6a8376c5d8bc05d2ef2c8ce3f3c0609a","tid":773774,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T03:33:25.000Z","msg":"樓主都幾on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人生流流長，唔打下工你點過日晨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日出街風花雪月你有一日會厭，比你環遊世界最多咪幾年時間，一樣會完。<br />\n<br />\n你錢又唔係特別多，得層樓就學人退休生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1218be74a0254fdca49f8ccbec7bddf26415415e","tid":773774,"uid":4402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59974fca6a8376c5d8bc05d2ef2c8ce3f3c0609a","tid":773774,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T03:33:25.000Z","msg":"樓主都幾on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人生流流長，唔打下工你點過日晨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日出街風花雪月你有一日會厭，比你環遊世界最多咪幾年時間，一樣會完。<br />\n<br />\n你錢又唔係特別多，得層樓就學人退休生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T03:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a40f6dc81f3a353b773eb579126e83a32b2cef03","tid":773774,"uid":55189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T03:44:47.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"e1034805ddf7bdd44e7ffde2d90c0adcf5f2ee54","tid":773774,"uid":129169,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1218be74a0254fdca49f8ccbec7bddf26415415e","tid":773774,"uid":4402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score